Littles Bed Set Mat Price: Rs.795

Key Features

  • Cylindrical Pillow for Extra Protection
  • Carry Bag
  • Sweat Absorber
  • 100% Cotton
  • Frills On Border
  • Soft Texture

A soft and cozy bed is a vital requirement to provide your little ones with luxurious comfort. Ensure a blissful night of sleep for your babies by gently placing them in this cute Baby Bed from Littles that is specifically made to let your kid have a peaceful night of sleep.

Sweat Absorber

Littles understands that babies tend to sweat profusely during their first years and has hence made this bed sweat absorbent to keep your kid fresh at all times.

100% Cotton

Made from pure cotton
column17:
this comfortable bed plays soft on your baby’s sensitive skin.

Soft Texture

It is difficult for young ones to sleep on a hard surface. The soft texture of this bed supports their delicate body.

Cylindrical Pillow

The bed comes with cylindrical pillows to provide extra protection and prevent your kid from falling off the bed while sleeping
column18:

Carry Bag
